channel.title: RuneScape F2P Money-Making
channel.description:
Does anyone know any nice, sort-of worth it (in terms of it being for F2P) money making guides or tactics? I've searched a few such as flipping (but starting off with NO cash), gathering ashes from firemaking, and even fletching (but forgot one had to be a member for this).
I've gotten back into it a little and wanted to give it a shot but realized that I had the account cleaned in terms of armor and weapons.
[IMG]http://puu.sh/murUj/407e8abd41.jpg[/img]

item.title: RuneScape F2P Money-Making
item.dc:creator: @Skyro Arbe
item.description:
@Skyro wrote:

To be honest, you’re not going to make near any money in f2p.

I’d say you buy member with irl and keep paying irl until you have enough money to use bonds.

As for making money I’d do some low level pvm (gwd) until you have a decent amount to merch.
